metadata.name: Frozen music I
metadata.description:
‘Music is liquid architecture; architecture is frozen music’  -  Johann Wolfgang von Goethe.

" Frozen music Ⅰ " is a music visualization artwork base on a solo piano piece  by Hungarian composer Franz Liszt, called “Liebestraum No. 3” (“Dream of Love”).

The music data has transferred into a moving construction. Each note casts the details of the construction. It uses a looping structure to represent the full piano piece.

1920 x 1080, Full video 260 seconds
A digital file will also be provided.
[Preview](https://twitter.com/i/status/1425950334510194688)
